@startuml
actor User
participant Website
participant "Flask API" as API
participant APIFree

User -> Website: Submit travel preferences\n(destination, dates, interests)
activate Website

Website -> API: POST /generate_itinerary\n(payload: preferences)
activate API

API -> APIFree: Request suggestions/generate itinerary\n(forward preferences)
activate APIFree

APIFree --> API: Return itinerary data + image URL/base64
deactivate APIFree

API --> Website: 200 OK\nitinerary JSON + image data
deactivate API

Website -> User: Display generated itinerary and image
deactivate Website
@enduml